    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Assemblages of non-stellar objects that are gravitationally bound and orbiting a star or star system. Planetary systems may include one or more planets and other bodies, such as dwarf planets, moons, asteroids, meteoroids, comets, and cosmic dust.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
